74
00:02:42,651 --> 00:02:44,462
The hospital's in the middle
of a crisis.

75
00:02:44,547 --> 00:02:47,196
I know... the dispenser
was out of body wash.

76
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,763
This is your new pager.

77
00:02:48,847 --> 00:02:50,199
