it's being paged,

78
00:02:50,283 --> 00:02:52,126
so maybe it's time to wrap up
this beauty routine

79
00:02:52,210 --> 00:02:53,820
and join me in the ED.

80
00:02:54,113 --> 00:02:55,897
How about I put on
some pants first?

81
00:02:58,711 --> 00:03:00,164
This is Casey,
our head nurse.

82
00:03:00,249 --> 00:03:02,165
Casey, this is Dr. Shin,
our new trauma surgeon.

83
00:03:02,250 --> 00:03:03,821
Oh, thank God.
Follow me.

84
00:03:03,905 --> 00:03:04,953
I got a kid who appears
to have swallowed

85
00:03:05,037 --> 00:03:06,389
some rare earth magnets.

86
00:03:06,522 --> 00:03:09,039
Ah, that's a sure
fire way to get attention, huh?

87
00:03:09,124 --> 00:03:10,952
Hi, I'm Dr. Shin.

88
00:03:12,254 --> 00:03:14,352
Casey, do you know the risks

89
00:03:14,437 --> 00:03:16,024
when adjusting multiple
magnets?

90
00:03:16,109 --> 00:03:18,836
Uh, if the magnets
were to connect internally,

91
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:20,134
